central intelligence, withdraw individually. Victory. Florence confirms it's over. Everyone injured, depleted, but alive. Florence: you improvised solution I couldn't plan, real teamwork. Runner: we listened. Velvet: it worked. Remedy: we trusted each other. Trust—not complete, not forgiveness, but effective working trust. Progress. Florence still apart but less isolated. Small, fragile, hard-won progress.
